{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>現場可見，山坡上有大樹折斷倒塌，壓毁下方一簡陋涼亭，鄰近的乒乓枱則無被波及，幸無釀傷亡。現場有工人透露，涼亭及乒乓球桌疑為僭建。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126637235518050304276439.jpeg/68kdJw-ZirfPegawoJEgePAB-k3hYwdNFkNV1SxDVdU\" alt=\"深水埗主教山配水庫附近，有大樹倒塌；警員封鎖現場。（梁偉權攝）\"><figcaption>深水埗主教山配水庫附近，有大樹倒塌；警員封鎖現場。（梁偉權攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126637231797571584542163.jpeg/A9NLHhBD4bfYkCFSEmyhGTQoT8xoVR25c-q_0Enqv9A\" alt=\"警方圍封附近一帶範圍。（梁偉權攝）\"><figcaption>警方圍封附近一帶範圍。（梁偉權攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126637228039344128295867.jpeg/GqYsp8TtOais7aTSNN4rUt57abPRcALqrkKgI5RCoCM\" alt=\"山坡上有大樹折斷倒塌。（梁偉權攝）\"><figcaption>山坡上有大樹折斷倒塌。（梁偉權攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126637224981565440045291.jpeg/VfF_fkFr18u9HpllaVVGQXimGEAaSx8iKCQ9KhIkPSo\" alt=\"深水埗主教山配水庫附近，有大樹倒塌。（梁偉權攝）\"><figcaption>深水埗主教山配水庫附近，有大樹倒塌。（梁偉權攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126637221596631040908213.jpeg/2Jk2n93csomCfK9RzYcwmiS3zIsIV45OcWX-DEtl_gw\" alt=\"山坡上有大樹折斷倒塌。（梁偉權攝）\"><figcaption>山坡上有大樹折斷倒塌。（梁偉權攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T14:23:44.418992+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":175,"images":5,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}